    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1243">
<l>iruntuḷḷi yeṉparita ṉeñcē parintuḷḷal </l>
<l> paitaṉōy ceytārka ṇil</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O my soul! why remain (here) and suffer thinking (of him)? There are no lewd thoughts (of you) in him who has caused you this disease of sorrow.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
